long_description: Add more fun to your camping experience with the Seattle Sports Terra Darts game. Each Terra Dart has a zippered pocket that you load with pebbles or a golf ball to create the throwing dart; closest Terra Dart to the center of the rope ring wins! The set includes 2 pair of darts, 2 rope rings and a convenient storage bag.
short_description: Add more fun to your camping experience with the Seattle Sports Terra Darts game.
